title: Women and Songs: Beginnings - 1999 2CD [flac]
description:
Women & Songs: Beginnings - 2CD - 1999 [flac]

A marvelous collection of songs sung by women, from Billy Holiday to Melissa Manchester. Includes most of the best American (and one Brit) female singers from the 60s and 70s, with a few from earlier. Some of the best and most recognizable voices in jazz, R&B and pop music. Simply a great collection of great tunes!
